cards.effect: You can Ritual Summon this card with "Mitsurugi Ritual". Monsters your opponent controls lose 800 ATK. You can reveal this card in your hand; Special Summon 1 "Mitsurugi" monster from your Deck, then Tribute 1 monster you control. You can only use this effect of "Ame no Habakiri no Mitsurugi" once per Duel. If this card is Tributed: You can add 1 "Mitsurugi" card from your Deck to your hand, except "Ame no Habakiri no Mitsurugi", then you can Special Summon this card. You can only use this effect of "Ame no Habakiri no Mitsurugi" once per turn.
cards.name: Ame no Habakiri no Mitsurugi

cards.effect:
When you activate this card, you can also Tribute 1 Reptile monster in your hand or field; apply 1 of these effects, or if you Tributed a monster at activation, you can apply both effects in sequence.
●Add 1 "Mitsurugi" monster from your Deck to your hand.
●Take 800 damage, then you can Special Summon 1 "Mitsurugi" monster from your hand or GY, but it cannot attack directly.
You can only activate 1 "Mitsurugi Prayers" per turn.
cards.name: Mitsurugi Prayers

cards.effect: When this card is activated: Add 1 "R.B." card from your Deck to your hand, except "R.B. Funk Dock". You can only use this effect of "R.B. Funk Dock" once per turn. You can only activate 1 "R.B. Funk Dock" per turn.
cards.name: R.B. Funk Dock
